(542, '03 Frontend Web Developers (HTML,Javascript, CSS)', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Very Attractive    ', 'Synova Solutions is seeking for 3 qualified candidates Frontend Web Developer to join our growing team. This role requires a focus on cross-discipline collaboration to bring the   strategic goals of our clients to life. That includes brainstorming with other discipline leads, rapid prototyping and leading the implementation of the selected ideas. \r\nWe are willing to offer excellent compensation packages including a base salary, bonus, benefits, etc...  ** Responsibilities:  â€¢	Builds software applications: Follows coding standards, builds appropriate unit tests, integration tests and deployment scripts; \r\nâ€¢	Assists in defining software architectures: Collaborates with leads to explore existing systems, determines areas of complexity, potential risks to successful implementation, learns the applications capabilities; \r\nâ€¢	Communicates continually with the client and project teams: Explains progress on the development effort; \r\nâ€¢	Owns success: Takes responsibility for successful delivery of the solutions; \r\nâ€¢	Contributes to continual improvement by suggesting improvements to user interface, software architecture or new technologies. ', ' JavaScript , CSS , HTML5 ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience ** Education & Qualification:  â€¢	Bachelor''s Degree in IT/ Computer Science or closely related field.  ** Experience:  â€¢	3+ years experience creating websites or applications with HTML, CSS, and Javascript/ jQuery; \r\nâ€¢	Experience delivering Frontend code for integration with Backend systems; \r\nâ€¢	Proficiency with Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator; \r\nâ€¢	A portfolio/ showcase of recent examples with code; \r\nâ€¢	Familiarity with version control (Git, SVN).  ** Skills:  â€¢	Strong customer service/ client service skills; \r\nâ€¢	Highly responsible, careful, hardworking, initiative and able to work under pressure; \r\nâ€¢	Good English skill.  ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here ** Salary:  â€¢	Very attractive. Commensurate with experience.  ** Benefits:  â€¢	Annual paid leave (exclude Vietnam public holidays): 15 days/ year plus sick leave; \r\nâ€¢	Annual Salary Review: Revised every 6 months; \r\nâ€¢	13th month salary and performance bonuses.  ', '2015-07-22 16:23:15', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/javascript-html5-03-frontend-web-developers-html-javascript-css'),
(543, 'IBM BPM Developer (J2EE,Java,SQL,CSS)', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Attractive    ', 'Develop IT solutions using a BPM suite. Some projects will require remote collaboration via the internet, other projects will require working directly with clients onsite at their place of business.  Responsibilities for this position - work directly with client and / or team to understand the requirements. Use up to date methodology to develop, test, debug, improve, document, and deploy solutions.   ** Description:    We are looking for the candidates with technical background such as Java Script, Business Process Management (BPM), J2EE application servers, Enterprise Content Management, good English skills, willing to learn, Candidates with experience in banking and insurance and a great attitude to work.  We are looking for dynamic, creative, and disciplined engineers to join our company.  This is your chance to get involved with a growing company with great people and fun, interesting projects.  We work with offshore and local clients developing Business Process Management solutions to help our clients manage their businesses more effectively.   We need developers who will work directly with customers for both offshore and onsite projects.  We are looking for people with strong knowledge of modern agile development technologies, with a solid technical background, and a strong desire to achieve excellence together. ', ' Java , SQL , J2EE ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Technical skills in any these areas will be valuable for applicants:  * Bachelor degree in IT \r\n* BPMN and BPM concepts \r\n* Java programming \r\n* J2EE application servers, especially websphere, Jboss \r\n* Web development - HTML, CSS, Javascript, Java based web development frameworks such as Struts. \r\n* SOA - familiar with concepts, experience consuming SOAP / REST services \r\n* SQL and general database interaction, especially Oracle, SQL Server, and DB2 \r\n* XML, XSL \r\n* Enterprise Content Management such as Filenet, Documentum, Oracle CM, etc  Candidates with experience in banking and insurance are strongly encouraged to apply.  If you have a strong technical background, good English skills, and a great attitude then we want to hear from you.   There will be opportunities for offshore outsource type work as well as onsite consulting work directly with customers here in Vietnam.    ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here * Public insurance and Additional health insurance \r\n* 40 hour/week, Public Holidays and Annual paid leave (13days). \r\n* 13th month salary \r\n* Quarterly bonus \r\n* IBM Certificate fee \r\n* Birthday gift \r\n* Home office supporting package  ', '2015-07-22 16:23:15', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/ibm-bpm-developer-j2ee-java-sql-css'),
