(545, 'PHP Developer with WORDPRESS experiences', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Up to 1,000 USD    ', 'Job description:  We are currently recruiting for the role of an PHP Developer with WORDPRESS experiences to join our ever-expanding team. This is a broad role, which includes theme and plugin development, as well as client support. You will be working closely with both the interconnect/it team and our clients'' various web teams.   Responsibilities: \r\nâ€¢	You will be exposed to CMS - WordPress development: updating & implementing WordPress themes and plugins \r\nâ€¢	Estimates the requirements and provide technical support for product/projects.  \r\nâ€¢	You will be working with medium and large scale development products/projects.  \r\nâ€¢	We are only fascinated in top candidates and our selection process has been designed to ensure that we choose those with a passion to grow their technical skills and to succeed in a team environment ', ' PHP , HTML5 , CSS ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Must have \r\nâ€¢	1-2 years working with web development, both backend and frontend \r\nâ€¢	Have a solid foundation of  PHP, HTML, CSS, JQuery, Ajax, MySQL and willing to learn new frameworks such as Backbone \r\nâ€¢	Ability to understand third party JavaScript code and customize them as needed \r\nâ€¢	W3C best practices  Nice to have:  â€¢	Having at least 1 year of working experience with WordPress is a BIG PLUS: theme development, plugin, theme customization \r\nâ€¢	Knowledge in Front-end implementation via HTML, HTML5, CSS, CSS3 and JavaScript \r\nâ€¢	Familiar with Backbone \r\nâ€¢	Preferred if having prior knowledge/experience with Facebook API, LinkedIn API, YouTube API, Google+ API, payment gateway API \r\nâ€¢	Using GIT, SVN is  a PLUS \r\nâ€¢	Have knowledge or experiences in UI/UX \r\nâ€¢	Experience with software development process Agile/Scrum/Kanban is a PLUS \r\nSoft skills:  \r\nâ€¢	Good English is a must: reading/writing. Good verbal English skills are a PLUS \r\nâ€¢	Timely manner \r\nâ€¢	Good decision maker \r\nâ€¢	Good problem solving skills \r\nâ€¢	Good time arrangement skills \r\nâ€¢	Motivated and hard-working, ready to take on any challenges \r\nâ€¢	Open-minded and good at adapting to frequent changes \r\nâ€¢	Be able to self-study, update new technology \r\nâ€¢	Ability to independent work directly with tasks. Strong responsibility. \r\nâ€¢	Professional attitude  ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here Our Company believes that motivation & personality of the employees are the only shortcut to the promotion of the corporate and contributions to the society. We will try our best to create a corporate environment where all employees can realize their dreams and goals. \r\nâ€¢	Featured benefits include:  \r\n- Have opportunity to work with overseas clients  \r\n- Join the dynamic, young and friendly project team  \r\n- Attend project training before working with clients directly if need  \r\n- Have the stable career path  \r\n- Attractive salary, based on skill and experience  \r\n- 13-month bonus program  \r\n- Additional bonus performance based bonus in addition to 13-month bonus  \r\n- Monthly event with company employees (play tennis, football,... and party). \r\n- Regular technical & soft skill training  \r\n- Providing Free coffee, tea, candy. \r\n- Happy events: kick off, birthday, Moon party \r\n- Technical seminar in the company  \r\n- Support for all sports activities: Football, Table tennis,.. \r\n- Yearly company trip  \r\n- Salary raises or bonus by work performance per 12 months  \r\n- All insurances according to Vietnamese Labor law   ', '2015-07-22 16:23:17', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/html5-css-php-developer-with-wordpress-experiences--2'),
(546, 'Senior Web And Mobile Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   1000-6000 USD    ', 'Choose to work from our offices in Da Nang, Ha Noi, or Ho Chi Minh City. You will work directly, in English, with the founders of new and rapidly growing Internet ventures to understand their vision and implement it on the web and on iPhone and Android smartphone platforms. You will use Extreme Programming and SCRUM agile development methods which include paired programming, Behavior Driven Development (BDD), Test Driven Development (TDD), and emergent business-value prioritized development. You will work in small teams of two to seven. You will enhance your skills in advanced javascript, Ruby on Rails, Python, iOS and Android development working with leading American companies. You will develop applications on Cloud platforms that can grow to support millions of users. You will stay on the cutting edge of Internet application development.  Other benefits include:  \r\n(1) end-of-year Tet bonus,  \r\n(2) 15 days annual leave,  \r\n(3) excellent health insurance,  \r\n(4) a 40-hour regular work week,  \r\n(5) a fun and flexible working environment in a modern office,  \r\n(6) Ability to work between our offices in Hanoi and Ho Chi Minh City, and Danang,  \r\n(7) Free office lunch.', ' Android , iOS , Ruby on Rails ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience - Years of experience: 1 year(s) Minimum career level  \r\n- Must have commercial experience working in Python, or Ruby on Rails or iOS or Android development.  \r\n- Education: We prefer a degree in computer science, mathematics or statistics from a top Vietnamese or foreign university.  \r\n- Excellent logic skills.  \r\n- Excellent Object oriented programming skills.  \r\n- Good verbal English communications skills.  \r\n- Familiar with Unix (Mac OSX, Solaris, or Linux command line).  \r\n- Familiar with test based development, refactoring, and programming in an IDE.  \r\n- Prefer experience developing applications on the Cloud, such as EC2, Heroku, Engine Yard, using relevant tools.  \r\n- Prefer knowledge of UX/UI best practices.  \r\n- Prefer experience working in an agile development environment using eXtreme Programming and/or SCRUM.  \r\n- Willing to work closely and continuously with other programmers, almost never programming alone. ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here - Best Agile training in Vietnam \r\n- Onsite parking, comfortable and professional office environment \r\n- Young and friendly colleagues \r\n- End-of-year Tet bonus \r\n- 15 days annual leave \r\n- Excellent health insurance \r\n- 40-hour regular work week - even when there is a major deadline next week \r\n- Freedom to take an afternoon nap ', '2015-07-22 16:23:17', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/android-ios-ruby-on-rails-senior-web-and-mobile-developer--3'),
(547, 'Senior iOS Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   You will love it    ', 'Weâ€™re looking for Senior iOS Developer to join our development team at KMS Technology', ' iOS , Mobile Apps , C++ ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience â€¢	Have at least 5 years of experience with C/C++ and Objective-C programming, which includes at least 2 years of experience with iOS development. \r\nâ€¢	Have at least 1 year of experience with game on iOS (QuartCore/OpenGLES). \r\nâ€¢	Have solid foundation knowledge and strong in OOAD. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience in dealing with Server Side using techniques such as RESTFul web services. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience in handling the performance and memory of Mobile App. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience in design iOS UIs using StoryBoard & AutoLayout. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience in UIs Customization (provide portfolios). \r\nâ€¢	Have experience with In-App Purchase & iCloud services. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience with Swift Language is a plus \r\nâ€¢	Have experience with Android development is a plus. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience with J2ME is a plus. \r\nâ€¢	Have experience with Unity Engine or Cocos2D-x is a plus. \r\nâ€¢	Familiar with AWS, Node.js and/or Rails is a plus \r\nâ€¢	Have experience in building multimedia-intensive applications and games in the relevant platform (e.g. WP7, Android etc.) is a plus. \r\nâ€¢	Competent in English and has the ability to communicate with the client effectively \r\nâ€¢	Passionate about mobile technologies and mobile development.  ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here In case you want to have a sneak-peek at our benefits:  \r\n- Salary range for software engineer up to $1,300+, senior software engineer up to $2,000+; 100% salary during probation period  \r\n- Performance appraisal twice a year  \r\n- Premium healthcare insurance (provided by AON this year) for you and your loved ones  \r\n- Onsite opportunities: short-term and long-term assignments in The United States of America  \r\n- Company trip in every summer, at least 2 team bu