(553, 'Senior PHP Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   16 Mil - 50 Mil VND pmth    ', 'Arrowsaint Ltd requires the services of a Senior PHP/Drupal Developer. While initially this will be a ''Work From Home'' role, it will likely be re-designated to an office position once our central Ho Chi Minh office is established.  The Initial Project:  \r\nYour first project is an exciting, new-age Reward Marketing application, incorporating two public websites, an online-market, Point-of-Sale mobile device portals, and a Transaction Payment portal.  The Role:  \r\nAs a Senior Drupal/PHP Developer, you will be involved in a fast paced environment working on a variety of projects as required by our international clients.  Working closely with our Solutions Architect, Front-End Developer and Project Manager, employing Web, Front and Back-End technologies including Javascript, AJAX, HTML, HTML5, CSS, AJAX, PHP, MySQL, PostgresSQL SAS, you will be involved in problem solving, maintaining existing code, writing new modules for web presences, financial services portals and mobile applications.  A significant proportion of your time will be directed to providing features for Drupal websites, and writing php code within the constraints of the Drupal Framework.  New projects will typicality commence agile and roll to water fall as the project matures. This role demands technical excellence, dedication and innovation.  An attractive all inclusive remuneration package value ranging between 16.000.000 to 50.000.000 VND Gross per month will be offered to the successful candidate based upon the experience and value that you can bring to the company.', ' PHP , Database , CSS ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience If you do not have ALL the skills listed below, we are still interested in hearing from you as we have a number of other roles that may better fit your skills set.  To 100% qualify for this role, the ideal candidate would have all the following skills and experience:   â–ª	To be able 