employ only the best. ', '2015-07-22 16:23:22', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/database-css-senior-php-developer'),
(554, 'Principal .Net Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Negotiate    ', 'Do you want the opportunity to work with a company that is a leader in digital media and commerce? Our dynamic team is looking to offer experienced developers an exciting and challenging role. A degree in computer science or information technology is required as a minimum and the successful candidate will possess a combination of the following skills, detailed below.   If you love cutting code for the web or mobile, and want to be challenged in diverse role then you should consider a role with Studio 60 in Ho Chi Minh City. We are only interested in top candidates and our selection process has been designed to ensure that we choose those with a passion to grow their technical skills and to succeed in a team environment.  We offer great salary package and benefits for the right candidates. Including monthly fitness\\personal development allowance, additional annual leave and a company bonus structure based on productivity and performance.', ' .NET , Android , iOS ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience 1.	Required: \r\n-	Good at verbal English \r\n-	At least 4 years'' experience in C# & .NET framework  \r\n-	Deep knowledge in building RESTful API using ASP.NET Web API +Entity framework \r\n-	Experienced in MS SQL Server database design and query \r\n-	Experienced in using GIT, tagging, branching and merging \r\n-	Basic experienced in building web application using ASP.NET MVC & jQuery \r\n-	Detail-oriented and have good problem solving skills \r\n-	Experienced in trouble shooting for complicated production system  2.	Desirable: \r\n-	Experienced in using / setting up Continuous Integration / Continuous Delivery using TeamCity, Jenkins etc. \r\n-	Knowledge and experienced in one of the modern JS MVC frameworks such as Angular JS \r\n-	Knowledge in some of the well-known Design Patterns such as Singleton, Factory Method, Dependency Injection, Repository, UoW etc. \r\n-	Experienced in building backend API for mobile apps ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here We offer great salary package and benefits for the right candidates. Including monthly fitness\\personal development allowance, additional annual leave and a company bonus structure based on productivity and performance. ', '2015-07-22 16:23:23', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/net-android-ios-principal-net-developer'),
