(556, 'Project managers', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Attractive package salary    ', 'We are looking for 3 web project managers for ecommerce projects (Magento/Demandware/Hybris). He should be fluent in English and can communicate with both customers and his/her team. He or she should be able to ensure a successful project delivery to our customer within pre-agreed time frames while maintaining a great team atmosphere.  Mandatory skills for this position: \r\no The project manager should aim to always deliver the best quality product to our customer within a pre-agreed time frame. For any issues/delays etc. the project manager will be the first person the customer will talk to, and he/she should be the first person to call the customer and explain the project. \r\no The project manager is not only a project executor but a guide for the customer, understanding their wishes and requirements, proposing alternative solutions while always ensuring that the result is in the best interest of both the customer and us. \r\no With the support from our Technical Manager, the project manager needs to understand the technical implication project requirements, be able to estimate a rough time frame and propose an implementation solution to the customer. The project manager therefore needs to be able to analyze and separate a project independently into smaller steps and milestones which then need to be assigned and followed upon with his team ', ' Project Manager , Business Analyst ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Job Requirement \r\nAll our project managers are supervised by a project director for internal training and project follow-up. We establish frequent meetings between project managers, the project director and business developers to share knowledge between project managers. \r\nResponsibilities \r\n- Managing full e-commerce projects from business requirements to roll-out and validation by the customer \r\n- Creating and editing customer documents such as functional specifications for customers, technical specifications for developers, UAT testing plan \r\n- Adherence to programming and testing standards, accuracy and creativity in finding efficient solutions to given requirements \r\n- Taking ownership for the quality of the projects, managing the quality control test team and validating the delivery of the project \r\n- Communication with customer including kick-off meeting, specifications validation, follow-up meetings during projects, UAT validation and support.  Requirements \r\n- At least two years experience as the project manager or Business Analyst \r\n- Experience in managing a team \r\n- Experienced in JavaScript, HTML/CSS, Ajax & optimizing MySQL is a plus \r\n- Strict dedication to delivering projects within deadlines while adhering to established quality and documentation standards \r\n- A good team player with excellent communication and interpersonal skills \r\n- Good spoken English is a requirement ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here â€¢ Opportunity to become the qualified project manager in one of the well â€“ known e-commerce solutions providers for international outourcing projects from Europe, US, China, Hong Kong, etc \r\nâ€¢ Opportunity to obtain the international certification on e-commerce solutions (Magento/Demandware/Hybris Certitficate) \r\nâ€¢ Friendly, young & dynamic working environment with many activities like football team, birthday party, happpy hours, company activites, company trips... \r\nâ€¢ Full package of insurance, PVI medical insurance and 13th month at the end of the year. \r\nâ€¢ Attractive package salary ', '2015-07-22 16:23:24', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/business-analyst-project-manager-project-managers'),
(557, 'Principal .NET Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   1600+ USD Gross    ', 'â€¢ Play effectively the Technical Architect role in the project \r\nâ€¢ Be responsible for the technical proposal, software design aspects and technical quality in the project. Design, document and implement the software architecture which addresses both functional and non-functional requirements of large scale system such as performance, scalability, security, extensibility, and reliability \r\nâ€¢ Review and improve on existing systems, making use of new technologies and methodologies to seek continual improvement for existing systems for the project \r\nâ€¢ Provide detail technical guidance and direction on project works to the team members/clients in the project, making sure that the delivery is in good quality in technical aspects \r\nâ€¢ Discuss architecture and design issues directly with clients. Be responsible, support and guide the project team to fulfill the detail design, code review, unit test; creating builds/releases, integration plan \r\nâ€¢ Implement and maintain the applications to support the requirements;  \r\nâ€¢ Support and maintain clients programs (Corporate & End-users);  \r\nâ€¢ Provide specialized clients users support.', ' ASP.NET , OOP , MVC ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience â€¢ Solid knowledge in ASP.NET (7+ years of experience)  \r\nâ€¢ Solid Knowledge in MVC, WCF, WPF, Signal R, Knockout JS, REST API  \r\nâ€¢ Solid knowledge about Design Pattern, OOP.  \r\nâ€¢ Good at English  \r\nâ€¢ Solid knowledge of Microsoft SQL Server OR MySQL and SQL language  \r\nâ€¢ Experience in working with MongoDB is a good plus \r\nâ€¢ Experience working with agile methodologies  \r\nâ€¢ Solid interpersonal and communication skills  \r\nâ€¢ Self-motivated, independent, committed ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here - Flat Organization  \r\n- Dynamic, Challenging, Exciting Environment  \r\n- Growth Opportunities  \r\n- Competitive Salary  \r\n- Might get full 13th month salary even if you join now. ', '2015-07-22 16:23:25', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/asp-net-oop-mvc-principal-net-developer'),
(558, 'System Engineer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   500 USD - 700 USD    ', '1. Development:  -	Plan, coordinate and implement the development. \r\n-	Research and develop automation systems of all Linux system for games and gameâ€™s platforms  2. Maintenance system:  -	Tracking system capacity (CPU, memory, disk space, networks etc.) and report/fix any issues \r\n-	Troubleshoot  and maintain online and offline Linux system \r\n-	Install software upgrades and security patches, and monitor for intrusion signs \r\n-	Security for all systems  3. Problem Resolving:  -	Perform problem resolution and provide on-call support for problems in system.  4. System design:  -	Assist with the planning and design of future systems architecture, to allow scaling to meet demand, optimize current architecture ', ' Linux , System Engineer , MySQL ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience 1. Educational qualifications :   - A Bachelor degree in computer science or related field \r\n  \r\n2. Relevant experience   - At least 1 years of experience in system engineer  3. Required skills \r\n  \r\n- 	Knowledge in network and application security focus on Linux, basic knowledge on Window \r\n-	Understand deeply web services: Apache, Nginx \r\n-	SQL database services: MySQL/MSSQL and other open-source database system. \r\n-	Scripting languages : Python, Shell  \r\n-	Understanding about automation deployment  4. Behaviours & attitude \r\n  \r\n-	Ability to work under pressure and time constraints. \r\n-	Must be self-motivated and able to achieve results. \r\n-	Learn quickly and work well within a team environment.  ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here What you can expect from us:   - Ample opportunities to grow. You get to propose your own ideas and see it through  \r\n- Work with passionate, talented and driven colleagues who get things done !  \r\n- Opportunity to work with variety of projects and products \r\n- Challenging and exciting problems that await you to solve ', '2015-07-22 16:23:25', 'http