(583, 'PHP Back-End Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Above 10m VND    ', 'JOB SUMMARY:	 \r\nResponsible for the strategic implementation of software using relevant programming techniques and languages, and development/maintenance of the company internal systems and internet/web solution. \r\nWork closely with and report to the Sr. Software Development Engineer and support them in managing the team and work flow by leading and coaching team members.  RESPONSIBILITIES:  \r\n- Develop Web for Back End. \r\n- Perform and develop quality programming and coding to written technical specifications, using relevant programming language. \r\n- Research, learn and write new software language to meet the need of any given project. \r\n- Support to create test plans and scripts, carry out bugs testing, identify defects and fix them where they were discovered or required. \r\n- Read and understand technical specifications \r\n- Interpret written business requirements and technical specification documents \r\n- Responsible for trouble-shooting application related issues and ensuring/ maintaining high performance and browser compatibility \r\n- Contribute to the technical direction and architecture of the software \r\n- Support in writing and maintaining documentation of software functionality', ' PHP , MySQL ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience - University/ College graduate in software engineering or relevant field \r\n- Minimum 3 year of relevant work experience is required \r\n- Experienced in web development, UI and usability understanding \r\n- Excellent logical thinking ability \r\n- Good at research and work under pressure \r\n- Excellent knowledge of OOP, PHP5, MySQL, MVC model \r\n- Excellent knowledge of codeigniter \r\n- Good at problem solving, collaboration and communication skills \r\n- Good level of English skills  Bonus skills \r\n- Have experience with or a basic understanding of Front-End development.  \r\n- Have Experience using HTML5 & CSS3 \r\n- Have Expe