(584, 'RTOS Software Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Negotiable    ', 'We are looking for RTOS Software Developers to perform software coding, testing and delivering to features developed in a Real-Time Operating System (RTOS). The RTOS includes functionalities for single sided, double sided, and cluster systems. You will: \r\n-	Involve in the full development cycle of products, from technical design, coding, testing, integration, and release \r\n-	Support customers on requested technical issues  \r\n-	Ensure that the assigned tasks are completed with high quality and on time \r\n-	Work together with RTOS software engineers in Italy, Australia, and Vietnam \r\n-	Follow Agile software development framework \r\n-	Perform other assigned tasks ', ' Agile , System Engineer , Tester ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience A University qualification in software engineering or a related degree, and have: \r\n-	Good knowledge about data structures, and algorithms \r\n-	Adaptability and flexibility in any programming language, \r\n-	More than 2 years of working experience on RTOS area would be a plus \r\n-	Fast and accurate troubleshooting skill \r\n-	Strong problem-solving skill, with a logical, analytical approach to work \r\n-	Passionate to develop career in a professional and multicultural work environment  \r\n-	Proactive and positive  \r\n-	Good communication \r\n-	Intermediate level of English \r\n-	High team work spirit and be willing to learn new technologies \r\n-	Interest to work in an Agile and Lean environment  ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here With  offices  situated  in  Melbourne  Australia,  Stockholm  Sweden,  Rome  Italy,  and  Ho  Chi  Minh  City Vietnam,  you  too can  be a  key  part of  our  success.  At DEK Technologies you will find yourself in an exciting career with: \r\n-	Attractive, competitive salary and incentives \r\n-	Opportunities for short and long-term training/work overseas  \r\n-	An excellent working environment in developing tomorrow