(585, 'Senior Front-end Developer', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Up to 1,800 USD    ', 'We''re looking for two types of frontend developers. Either those with advanced Javascript skills (node.js, SPA, React, Angular, Gulp, immutable data, etc.) or those with advanced CSS and design skills. If you have both of those - even better - you''ll get paid more.', ' JavaScript , HTML5 , CSS ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Must Haves:  \r\n* Experience working with single-page JS web app.  \r\n* HTML5 API experience  \r\n* Fluency in Javascript  \r\n* Fearless: not afraid to learn and push your limits  \r\n* Batteries charged: you don''t need close management.  \r\n* Free thinking: willing to challenge the status quo with facts - not just feelings  Nice to have:  \r\n* ES6 - babel.js  \r\n* Javascript unit test and interface testing  \r\n* Master in browser compatibility (IE9 is our weakest link)  \r\n* CSS Processors  \r\n* Using node.js (Gulp, Grunt or Yeoman) for build/dev automation  \r\n* Git and continuous deployment  We''re looking for people at all levels:  \r\n* Junior: $650-$900  \r\n* Intermediate: $800-$1400  \r\n* Senior: $1100-$1800 ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here *** The opportunity \r\n- Working with a product focused team in Vietnam that sells to the US market \r\n- Working with the best, most innovative thinkers in the region \r\n- Learning and applying the Lean process to software development  *** What can we offer you? \r\n- A position in product focused company \r\n- A chance to learn product development process from Lucas Jans \r\n- 13th month Salary \r\n- National holidays, a full week off in the summer and 2 weeks of flex time \r\n- Need a book, we''ll buy it. Need an educational course, it''s yours.  ', '2015-07-22 16:23:47', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/javascript-html5-css-senior-front-end-developer--5'),
(586, 'iOS Team Leader &amp; Developers', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Above 14m VND    ', 'LARION Computing, one of Vietnam''s 30 Leading IT companies in 2014, is looking for iOS Team Leader & iOS Developers to join our outstanding software development team. The iOS Team Leader will collaborate with a dynamic and creative team of developers at various stages of development, look to innovate and improve every aspect of each application.  \r\n- Communicate with PM to clear all requirements, analyzing and design system. \r\n- Participate in developing project plan, project schedule, ensure project quality and tracking status. Ensuring the performance of the staff is of a high standard. \r\n- Instruct developer to solve technical problems. \r\n- Join in training to improve the technical level and the ability to work of members', ' iOS , Mobile Apps , HTML5 ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience **TECHNICAL SKILLS \r\n- Proven experience in developing mobile applications running on smart phones and tablet. \r\n- Programming skills â€“ Apple iOS SDK, HTML5, Swift, Objective C \r\n- Good System Design & Analysis skills. \r\n- Good knowledge of IOS  **NON-TECHNICAL SKILLS \r\n- Good Ability to comprehend, analyse and express \r\n- Good Attitude, Clear Thinking Mind, Adaptive and Interactive \r\n- Good Verbal & Writing Skills, Presentation Skills \r\n- Good Inter-Personal Relation Skills, Leadership skills \r\n- Able to handle daily work independently with little supervision] ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here Benefits \r\n- Lunch free \r\n- Parking free  \r\n- Birthday gift \r\n- Good opportunity to be trained and work with an experienced and professional staff \r\n- Annual vacation (Company pay) \r\n- Sport clubs ( football, badminton) ', '2015-07-22 16:23:47', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/mobile-apps-html5-ios-team-leader-developers'),
