(589, 'Senior Dynamic AX Engineer (05 vacancies)', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Negotiable    ', 'TMA has constantly delivered to our customer in high quality for enterprise solutions and going to establish a sizable offshore Dynamic AX development center for a New Zealand customer. We are looking for talent Dynamic AX developer who has strong .NET background and yearsâ€™ experience in MS Dynamic system and experience in customize and implement demand customer business workflow base on Dynamic AX. Good at problem solving skill and communication skill is a must.', ' .NET , C# , Oracle ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Programming Skills:  -       C#  \r\n-       .Net Framework (3.5/4.0) \r\n-       WCF  \r\n-       ASP.NET Web API  \r\n-       .NET windows forms \r\n-       .NET windows services \r\n-       ADO.NET and Entity Framework \r\n-       Microsoft Visual Studio 2008 & 2010 IDE  \r\n-       Proficient in the use of SQL (both DML and DDL) \r\n-	 3+ years of experience full time in MS Dynamic 2012 as developer or business consultant \r\n  \r\nImplementation:  -       Database design methodologies and tools (aka 3NF, ERD) \r\n-       Test Driven Development, familiar with NUnit, MOQ,  \r\n-       Continuous Integration using Cruise Control/Hudson \r\n-       Practical knowledge of using Dependency Injection tool e.g. sprint.net, castle  \r\n  \r\nDesirable:  -       Oracle PLSQL  \r\n-       Microsoft VB 6.0 \r\n-       Certified MS Dynamic AX 2012 is an advantage  Note:  â€¢	Salary negotiation. \r\nâ€¢	Salary range will depend on ability and experience working. \r\nâ€¢	More details will be discussed in the interview process.  \r\nâ€¢	Deadline to apply: 07 Aug 2014   ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here As one of the leading IT companies in Vietnam, we value our people and always want to support our staff with all the best conditions that we can. Here come some of the featured benefits, if you want to learn more about what we are offering, let''s join us today!  