(590, 'Drupal Architect (Software Architect)', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Above 30m VND    ', 'RMIT Vietnam is seeking a highly motivated and dedicated person to function as Drupal Architect (Software Architect). This position will be responsible for strategic design; development and implementation of efficient information systems and operations systems in support of network; telecommunications and core organizational functions.  The Drupal Architect will gain organizational commitment for all systems and software plans, as well as evaluate and select all technologies required to complete those plans. In addition, this role is responsible for providing technical leadership across the organization, from strategic decision making to project planning and execution. \r\nDependent on previous experience and academic achievement, the successful candidate, will be offered an attractive remuneration package comprising of:  â€¢	Monthly Base Salary in the range of 31,300,000 VND - 34,500,000 VND gross per month.  \r\nâ€¢	Monthly meal 680,000 VND and clothing 416,000 VND allowances  \r\nâ€¢	Private Medical Insurance  \r\nâ€¢	13th month Tet bonus ', ' PHP , JavaScript , SQL ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Mandatory \r\nâ€¢	Experience in all phases of software development including design, configuration, testing, debugging, implementation, and support of large-scale, business centric and process based applications \r\nâ€¢	Proficient in programming languages including PHP, JavaScript, HTML, Ajax, and Drupal/Symfony framework \r\nâ€¢	Good experience with Linux systems administration and web server / DB management (MS SQL, MySQL) \r\nâ€¢	Understanding of hosting needs and constraints for development (Load balancing and session management, CDN and URL management, caching mechanism, etc.) \r\nâ€¢	Proven ability to debug or troubleshoot complex problems while providing effective progress communications and fault escalation procedures. \r\nâ€¢	Proven ability to successfully partici