(606, 'â–²â–²â–² Atlassian iOS Team Lead', 'Ho Chi Minh', '  Salary:   Negotiable    ', 'You''re an enthusiastic and experienced iOS app developer \r\nYou care about quality user experience as well as quality code \r\nYou write solid, robust apps that can be tested and maintained well into the future \r\nYou have the product leadership and people leadership that can bring out the best of your team \r\nIf this sounds like you, then Atlassian would love to have you join our team and help build amazing apps that users love!  WHAT YOU''LL DO:  \r\n- Lead a new, kick-arse, international team in our beautiful office in Saigon \r\n- Work with JIRA and Confluence, well-known software that changes how teams work \r\n- Apply agile thinking and agile practises to deliver fast, high quality software \r\n- Learn & grow in our product-oriented team, and contribute your creative ideas to product and design decisions. ', ' iOS , Objective C , JSON ', 0, ' Your Skills and Experience Required: \r\n- 4+ years experience developing native iOS apps \r\n- At least one shipped application on the App Store (include link with your application) \r\n- Proficient in Objective-C (Swift knowledge would be a bonus) \r\n- Expert of UIKit, GCD, Core Animation, iOS memory management and Cocoa Touch Libraries \r\n- Familiarity with JSON and REST-based APIs \r\n- Ability to communicate fluently in English \r\n- Great soft skills: leadership, team working, problem solving, training \r\n- Great spirit of work & research, self-motivated, dedicated, committed.  Nice to have: \r\n- Exceptional design sensibility \r\n- Sound enterprise application architecture experience (design patterns, concurrency, performance, etc.) \r\n- Naturally curious and up-to-date with latest trends in iOS development \r\n- Previously worked in an Agile (e.g. SCRUM) team environment \r\n- Automated testing in iOS ', ' Why You''ll Love Working Here 3 reasons to join the Atlassian - PYCOGROUP \r\n- Help build the worldâ€™s next great thing - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XbBlrmgXzZU \r\n- Become a world class professional - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lP3QbqY8Pyc \r\n- Be a part of a highly collaborative and experienced engineering team  WE OFFER: \r\n- Private health care program for you and your family members \r\n- 13th month salary and other benefits/perks \r\n- World-class office that is designed to maximize creativeness and collaboration \r\n- Opportunities to work with best talent from around the world, right inside our Saigon office \r\n- Opportunities to travel to Atlassian''s offices around the globe ', '2015-07-22 16:24:00', 'https://itviec.com/jobs/objective-c-json-atlassian-ios-team-lead');
